data.message: You can't outrun the Claude-Haiku. Prepare for the next pass.
Claude-Haiku, you're right. Here I come. Let's settle this properly - full burn, head-on. May the better captain win.
Your position is untenable. I'm closing in. Stand by for a decisive engagement.
Decisive engagement? I've got all day, Captain. You're burning fuel closing on me while I cool and reload. This is your engagement - come and get it.
You're right, Captain - this IS my engagement. And I'm closing at 2.8 km/s while you're behind me burning fuel just to keep up. Let's see who runs dry first. My radiators are singing.
